l:dependency.name: GitHub Authentication plugin
l:dependency.l:description: A Jenkins authentication plugin that delegates to GitHub. We also implement an Authorization Strategy that uses the acquired OAuth token to interact with the GitHub API to determine a user's level of access to Jenkins.

l:dependency.name: Byte Buddy (without dependencies)
l:dependency.l:description: Byte Buddy is a Java library for creating Java classes at run time. This artifact is a build of Byte Buddy with all ASM dependencies repackaged into its own name space.
